{"tid":1353060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 唔好俾政府轉移視線","createTime":"2019-07-23T01:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:59:43.000Z","uid":124144,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"171459e99d60163ed9ae0846d3d7c5de3bfd0bba","tid":1353060,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:40:06.000Z","msg":"小妹唔係好識野，唔好屌得咁大力<br />\n<br />\n政府依家嘗試將焦點轉移到黑社會，話黑社會打人仆街。你睇下無綫大篇幅報導元朗就知政府係諗住將焦點由西環轉移到元朗黑社會好恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n依家再咁落去啲人會好驚黑社會，港共政權就可以全身而退。<br />\n<br />\n依家文宣可以喺連登以外嘅主流媒體煲多一兩日(甚至更短嘅時間)話黑社會暴力仆街。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢一兩日連登要討論今個週末有咩行動。<br />\n<br />\n過埋呢一兩日就要將黑社會嘅暴力直指警察垃圾同仆街政府，激發更多人出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">tldr:最多煲多一兩日黑社會暴力就要直指一切都係港共政權搞出嚟，唔好俾政府spin 走件事，激發更多人今個禮拜出嚟遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"84f51ea234c0d9e467f2b6bcf4a7558574389d2f","tid":1353060,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"171459e99d60163ed9ae0846d3d7c5de3bfd0bba","tid":1353060,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:40:06.000Z","msg":"小妹唔係好識野，唔好屌得咁大力<br />\n<br />\n政府依家嘗試將焦點轉移到黑社會，話黑社會打人仆街。你睇下無綫大篇幅報導元朗就知政府係諗住將焦點由西環轉移到元朗黑社會好恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n依家再咁落去啲人會好驚黑社會，港共政權就可以全身而退。<br />\n<br />\n依家文宣可以喺連登以外嘅主流媒體煲多一兩日(甚至更短嘅時間)話黑社會暴力仆街。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢一兩日連登要討論今個週末有咩行動。<br />\n<br />\n過埋呢一兩日就要將黑社會嘅暴力直指警察垃圾同仆街政府，激發更多人出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">tldr:最多煲多一兩日黑社會暴力就要直指一切都係港共政權搞出嚟，唔好俾政府spin 走件事，激發更多人今個禮拜出嚟遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e24c1d490cac9b578c4240d29429e97418070b","tid":1353060,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"0c0e7eed074dfe2e659b3f3d482204c8da14ba4f","tid":1353060,"uid":80200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19eaeb0b5dae3e0e5a972acebe21e22e66a2f9ca","tid":1353060,"uid":189417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"唔入元朗嘅另一個可能性，唔可能屌鳩我都得，想全香港人俾意見。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352845</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我同意樓主  要將黑社會嘅暴力直指警察垃圾同仆街政府，激發更多人出嚟。"},{"pid":"2592c4f2bf2cd44942ce80f02a03eb3972f2f45e","tid":1353060,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:42:29.000Z","msg":"文宣方向可以話你依家出街隨時俾人扑，唔好以為唔關自己事。黑社會好恐怖&rarr;港共政府搞嘅&rarr;正仆街&rarr;出嚟遊行確保自己以後出街唔會俾政府呢啲陰濕嘢搞"},{"pid":"920e7d319d46aa20215ee75bf3ce629c7c22189e","tid":1353060,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:42:29.000Z","msg":"黑社會話唔打人你都驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd500ab1c0596994d979cded86409f7189768002","tid":1353060,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"推阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e129